      *================================================================
      *
      ** Copyright insertion
      *
     C                     MOVEACPY@      BIS@   80
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           @HCONT  1
      *
     C                     SETOF                     10
      *
      ** Read FTCONTPD until EOF reached or until no outstanding batch
      ** is found.
      *
     C                     READ FTCONTPD                 10
     C           *IN10     DOWNE'1'
     C           COSTAT    ANDNE'R'
     C                     READ FTCONTPD                 10
     C                     END
      *
      ** If EOF is reached then no Outstanding batch.
      *
     C           *IN10     IFEQ '1'
     C                     MOVE 'N'       @HCONT
     C                     END
      *
      ** If a record with COSTAT = R is found, there is an outstanding
      ** batch.
      *
     C           COSTAT    IFEQ 'R'
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       @HCONT
     C                     END
      *
     C                     SETON                         LR
